l": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Tightens all precision windows by 40% on Premium+ jobs. Forces real investment in protection perks. The cost of overreaching is built into the modifier itself."}, {"id": "gdd_reputation_system", "label": "Reputation System", "file_type": "document", "source_file": "UPHOLSTERY_GDD_v8.txt", "source_location": "\u00a75", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null}, {"id": "gdd_toolbox_perk_system", "label": "Toolbox Pick-5 Perk System", "file_type": "document", "source_file": "UPHOLSTERY_GDD_v8.txt", "source_location": "\u00a76", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null}, {"id": "gdd_bolt_bespoke", "label": "Bolt vs Bespoke Perk Tiers", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "UPHOLSTERY_GDD_v8.txt", "source_location": "\u00a76.2", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Bolt perks are reliable and accessible; Bespoke are conditional and stronger. Bespoke conditions like 'Good or better only' mean skilled players benefit more \u2014 the system rewards competence, not just spending."}, {"id": "gdd_economy", "label": "Economy System", "file_type": "document", "source_file": "UPHOLSTERY_GDD_v8.txt", "source_location": "\u00a77", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null}, {"id": "gdd_followers", "label": "Followers Currency", "file_type": "document", "source_file": "UPHOLSTERY_GDD_v8.txt", "source_location": "\u00a77.2", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null}, {"id": "gdd_money_sinks", "label": "Money Sinks", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "UPHOLSTERY_GDD_v8.txt", "source_location": "\u00a77.3", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Perk charges are the primary money sink. Keeps high earners spending continuously rather than accumulating idle wealth."}, {"id": "gdd_shop", "label": "Shop", "file_type": "document", "source_file": "UPHOLSTERY_GDD_v8.txt", "source_location": "\u00a78", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null}, {"id": "gdd_talkogram", "label": "Talkogram Activity Feed (Post-Launch)", "file_type": "document", "source_file": "UPHOLSTERY_GDD_v8.txt", "source_location": "\u00a79", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null}, {"id": "gdd_player_progression", "label": "Player Progression", "file_type": "document", "source_file": "UPHOLSTERY_GDD_v8.txt", "source_location": "\u00a710", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null}, {"id": "gdd_player_house", "label": "Player House (Post-Launch)", "file_type": "document", "source_file": "UPHOLSTERY_GDD_v8.txt", "source_location": "\u00a710.1", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null}, {"id": "gdd_daily_contracts", "label": "Daily Contracts", "file_type": "document", "source_file": "UPHOLSTERY_GDD_v8.txt", "source_location": "\u00a710.3", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null}, {"id": "gdd_penalty_system", "label": "Penalty System", "file_type": "document", "source_file": "UPHOLSTERY_GDD_v8.txt", "source_location": "\u00a711", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null}, {"id": "gdd_special_events", "label": "Special Events", "file_type": "document", "source_file": "UPHOLSTERY_GDD_v8.txt", "source_location": "\u00a713", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null}, {"id": "gdd_design_pillars", "label": "Design Pillars", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "UPHOLSTERY_GDD_v8.txt", "source_location": "\u00a71", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Four pillars: (1) Skill has a ceiling, loadout raises the floor; (2) Every job is a bet; (3) Reputation is earned not bought; (4) The board is shared, the grind is personal."}, {"id": "gdd_minigame_interface", "label": "Minigame Common Interface", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "UPHOLSTERY_GDD_v8.txt", "source_location": "\u00a74", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "All minigames share Start(container,config)->GetResult()->Cleanup() API. Results: FAIL->PASS->GOOD->PERFECT. Worst result in chain becomes final result."}, {"id": "gdd_compound_failure", "label": "Compound Failure Cost Design", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "UPHOLSTERY_GDD_v8.txt", "source_location": "\u00a711.2", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Failure costs: rep loss + tool charges lost + no pay + time lost. No direct money deduction \u2014 charge burn scales with loadout investment. Intentional design so riskier equipped attempts cost more to fail."}], "edges": [{"source": "gdd_core_gameplay_loop", "target": "gdd_shared_job_board", "relation": "references", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "UPHOLSTERY_GDD_v8.txt", "source_location": "\u00a72", "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "gdd_core_gameplay_loop", "target": "gdd_toolbox_perk_system", "relation": "references", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "UPHOLSTERY_GDD_v8.txt", "source_location": "\u00a72", "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "gdd_core_gameplay_loop", "target": "gdd_minigames", "relation": "references", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "UPHOLSTERY_GDD_v8.txt", "source_location": "\u00a72", "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "gdd_core_gameplay_loop", "target": "gdd_reputation_system", "relation": "references", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "UPHOLSTERY_GDD_v8.txt", "source_location": "\u00a72", "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "gdd_job_system", "target": "gdd_shared_job_board", "relation": "referenc